content: I'm looking for some decorating ideas for my new home. I've been thinking of a backyard BBQ party to break in the new place. Do you have any suggestions for outdoor furniture and decorations that would be suitable for a family with a two-year-old? By the way, our real estate agent, Rachel, sent us an email with a list of new listings that fit our criteria on Tuesday of next week, which really helped us find our dream home.
